snippet.title: Green Hell VR – Co-Op Mode | Release Date Trailer | Meta Quest 2, 3/3S, PSVR2
snippet.description:
Survivors, it’s time to face the Amazon jungle, together!

Check out our new Co-Op Release Date trailer, showcasing the ultimate team survival experience for Meta Quest 2, 3, 3S, and PSVR2.

Co-Op mode arrives on December 16, 2024! Gather your team and get ready for an unforgettable journey!

Build shelters, hunt for food, and explore the depths of the jungle with up to three friends. Team up to tackle every challenge together and make the most of your survival adventure.

Get the game here:

Meta Quest: https://www.meta.com/en-gb/experiences/3815577785147028/
PSVR2: https://store.playstation.com/pl-pl/concept/10004102

Follow us for the latest updates and exclusive content:
https://discord.gg/uNqRHyDBuW / discord
https://x.com/GreenHellVR / greenhellvr

It’s time to survive, together! 💪

#greenhellvr #psvr2 #vr #vrcoop #vrgame #survival
